name: Devious Licks Gold
description: "Devious Licks is an ambitious project aiming to combine the exciting nature of thievery, gaming, and the immutability of the blockchain all mixed with an old school RPG vibe. Our project consists of 3 main launches; 2 NFT collections and a token. Our current focus is on NFT staking, which will come alive when our dGold token fully launches (tier 2). Holders of our first NFT collection (LICKs) will be able to stake and earn dGold with varying APR based on the rarity value of their NFTs."
